src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Numbers Evening' game
02 Nov 2019, 23:10 by The Associated Press
CRANSTON, R.I. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday evening's drawing of the Rhode Island Lottery's "Numbers Evening" game were:
8-1-6-4
(eight, one, six, four)
